<sect1 id="dir_e5915e51628795b15babf33bf45a77aa_1autotoc_md122">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::spawn::logic</title><para>Spawn conditions and strategies for controlling entity creation.</para>
<para>This namespace provides the policy interfaces and implementations for the spawn system. Conditions determine <emphasis>when</emphasis> to spawn, while strategies handle <emphasis>how</emphasis> to configure spawned entities.</para>
</sect1>
